@sp6370 Great! I am assigning this to you.

A better way to solve this with little code, is to add support via an env variable and K8s annotation instead - same as it was done for APP_API_TOKEN: https://docs.dapr.io/operations/security/app-api-token/. Maybe call this new one APP_API_TOKEN_HEADER.

Don't forget to also create a new functional test and update the docs as part of the PR.
